comments: Wiggins (GSW) maintains a legal guarding position on Beal (WAS) as he turns the ball over.
Green (GSW) reaches in and makes clean contact with the ball defending Beal's (WAS) drive to the basket.
Hachimura (WAS) reaches through the net/rim and makes contact with the ball during Wiggins' (GSW) shot attempt.

Green (GSW) jumps vertically contesting Hachimura's (WAS) shot attempt at the basket and gets his hand on the ball.  Green's hand remains on the ball until Hachimura returns to the floor and a jump ball is correctly whistled.
Beal (WAS) gathers the ball and takes three steps as he drives to the basket.
Green (GSW) brings his arm forward and marginal contact occurs with Beal (WAS) during his shot attempt at the basket.
Westbrook (WAS) commits a take foul on Curry (GSW).
Hachimura (WAS) commits a take foul on Curry (GSW).
Wiggins (GSW) makes contact to Beal's (WAS) head and affects his jump shot attempt.
Avdija (WAS) is in a legal guarding position and incidental contact occurs with Lee (GSW) as he turns the ball over.
Wiggins (GSW) commits a take foul on Beal (WAS).
